p: GC-FID analysis was carried out using the < <Chromateck-Crystall 5000 > > GC chromatograph with the DAG-2M automatic dispenser. GC separation was performed in a SolGelWax column with the dimensions of 30 m × 0.25 mm × 0.5 µm; gas mobile phase - helium; speed - 25 cm/sec; temperature range - 185–230 °C.
